{"tha-ap98:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap98:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap98:0.3":"Tipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap98:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap98:1.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap98:1.3":"Patalim haritam disva, ","tha-ap98:1.4":"tini pupphani okirim. ","tha-ap98:2.1":"Patitapattani ganhitva, ","tha-ap98:2.2":"bahi chaddesaham tada; ","tha-ap98:2.3":"Antosuddham bahisuddham, ","tha-ap98:2.4":"suvimuttam anasavam. ","tha-ap98:3.1":"Sammukha viya sambuddham, ","tha-ap98:3.2":"vipassim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap98:3.3":"Patalim abhivadetva, ","tha-ap98:3.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap98:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap98:4.2":"yam bodhimabhipujayim; ","tha-ap98:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap98:4.4":"bodhipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap98:5.1":"Samantapasadika nama, ","tha-ap98:5.2":"terasasimsu rajino; ","tha-ap98:5.3":"Ito tettimsakappamhi, ","tha-ap98:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap98:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap98:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap98:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap98:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap98:8.1":"Tipupphiyattherassapadanam chattham. "}